    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i>我不是医生……但我懂药理学。</i><br><i>我不是理学学士……但我懂有机化学。</i><br><i>我不是MBA毕业生……但我懂管理。</i><br><i>我不是注册会计师……但我懂账务。</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300150/extras/99802ad3b372444965ba6df333cd8a3f.avif?t=1771615928\" width=1268 height=354 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >走进柜台，经营属于你自己的药店！<br>从核对处方到管理复杂的库存，每一个决定都会影响你的底线——以及你的声誉。<br><strong>身兼收银员、经理、会计和健康顾问数职于一身——你就是药剂师。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300150/extras/2a4a948284b1abdffd841cb75d822e04.avif?t=1771615928\" width=438 height=107 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300150/extras/7d8e49b8559611a4d216a26a7f5cb51c.poster.avif?t=1771615928\" width=780 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300150/extras/7d8e49b8559611a4d216a26a7f5cb51c.webm?t=1771615928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300150/extras/7d8e49b8559611a4d216a26a7f5cb51c.mp4?t=1771615928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>我将把人类的福祉和减轻痛苦作为我的首要关切。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >门铃响起，队伍越来越长。无论是救命的处方药还是简单的止痛药，你的工作就是把正确的产品交到顾客手中。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>进货与检索：</strong>在库存中寻找特定的药丸、糖浆和软膏。如果货架上没有，你就卖不了！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>扫描与结账：</strong>管理收银机，处理付款，高效打包物品以保持队伍流动。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>处理处方：</strong>分析、验证并在货架上找到正确的药物。小心假处方！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300150/extras/5d143c52b8751901a4759eeb7beb8716.avif?t=1771615928\" width=438 height=107 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300150/extras/4bd5a1bd54f353f17278c3c73931559a.poster.avif?t=1771615928\" width=780 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300150/extras/4bd5a1bd54f353f17278c3c73931559a.webm?t=1771615928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300150/extras/4bd5a1bd54f353f17278c3c73931559a.mp4?t=1771615928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>我将尽我所能运用我的知识、经验和技能，以确保所有患者获得最佳结果。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >并不是每个人都想好了要买什么药，或者带着处方单进来。<br>患者会带着感冒、过敏和疼痛到来，寻求你的专业意见。你是专家——现在是证明这一点的时候了。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>分析症状：</strong>仔细倾听患者的主诉。无论是干咳、发烧还是神秘的皮疹，你都需要找出根本原因。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>推荐正确的疗法：</strong>筛选你的药物知识，建议正确的非处方治疗方案。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>声誉就是一切：</strong>提供正确的建议可以提升药店评分并赢得客户的忠诚度。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300150/extras/7da3f932f2b7b096ad922299439bfcf1.avif?t=1771615928\" width=438 height=107 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300150/extras/24bd4d12f2ca3d19d568ba2eb437aa01.poster.avif?t=1771615928\" width=780 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300150/extras/24bd4d12f2ca3d19d568ba2eb437aa01.webm?t=1771615928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300150/extras/24bd4d12f2ca3d19d568ba2eb437aa01.mp4?t=1771615928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>我将拥护并倡导改善患者护理的变革。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你从一家库存有限的狭窄店铺开始。当你赚取利润后，重新投资以构建你的愿景。保持货架充足和结账队伍简短，以获得五星好评。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>获取执照：</strong>解锁销售新药和受控物质的许可。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>制定价格：</strong>在利润率和客户满意度之间取得平衡。提高畅销品的价格以快速获利，或提供折扣以建立长期忠诚度。如果你漫天要价，不满的顾客会空手而归。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>装修与扩建药店：</strong>从小的平面图开始，购买更多空间以吸引和容纳更多顾客。用新的货架来存放你的药物和其他家具。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>我承诺通过履行这一誓言，终身致力于通过药学专业为他人服务。</i></p>",
